Following example deployed as WAR under Catalina:

public abstract class BaseWebService {
    ...

    @PostConstruct
    public void init() {
        logger.info("init called");
    }
}

@WebService(...) 
public class MyWebService extends BaseWebService {
  ...
}

Upon deployment of MyWebService no "init called" ever appears in the logs.

It looks like a duplicate of 45285 but we've tested this on 6.0.18, 6.0.19, 6.0.20 and 6.0.35 and found it not to work.

Moving the init method into MyWebService is a workaround but results in a messy codebase.
